commit_message:
Install hook fails on public/private address not found

Every successful hook execution calls assess_status that end up
calling network_get_primary_address. Sometimes during install,
Juju is not ready to give the addresses that causes the CalledProcessError.

* Added try and except to run assess_status;
* Log execution errors with traceback;
* Added unit-tests for main hook execution;
* Install hook doesn't run assess_status.

Closes-Bug: #1924780
Change-Id: Ibdfcc4ebe595252938745204f1d2bce038c3ac7e
